<section id="reference-wizards-hibernate_configuration_file">
  <title>Hibernate configuration file</title>
  <para>
    A Hibernate configuration file is necessary to perform such tasks as reverse engineering, query prototyping and to use Hibernate Core and Annotations. The file can be created manually or with the aid of a wizard as displayed in <xref linkend="figure-hibernate_configuration_file_01"/>
  </para>
